latestPosts.caption:
👋 We see a lot of new faces here, so we thought it was time to reintroduce ourselves. We’re a small (but mighty) all-female team based in New Hampshire and are probably behind some of your favorite local brands’ social media accounts. 👀

How do we stay efficient with just a few of us? Well, we have a few immutable laws we like to live by when working with our clients. 😏

1️⃣ Communication: It really is the key to our most successful accounts. We want to know EVERYTHING about your business, and we want you to trust our work.

2️⃣ You Get What You Give: Our best results come from working with clients who are as passionate about growth and learning as we are! We value positivity and collaboration every step of the way.

3️⃣ Results-Driven: Your success is our success. Data and performance metrics guide our strategies to ensure we deliver the results you need to see your brand grow.

4️⃣ Dream Big: We aim for the stars. 🌟 Thinking outside of the box and making bold moves has led us to some incredible outcomes, and we don’t plan to stop any time soon!

Drop one of your immutable laws in the comments for us to add to our list. 👇

If you’re new here, thanks for the follow! Feel free to introduce yourself—we hope you learn a thing or two from our posts!

latestPosts.caption:
We’ve all had a bad post or two. 😅 Thankfully, we’ve grown from posting “Happy Monday” just to get a post out.

By now, we’ve all heard it’s better to post something with substance, but what does that actually mean? To our team, it means sharing educational posts in a story-telling way. Include blurbs about your brand story, who makes up the team, and share facts like “our most popular brunch item.”

Want to get even deeper? Be transparent. 👀 Tell a story about a problem you faced and how you overcame it, making you the expert for people to trust.

Do you remember one of your first posts? Do you cringe looking at it? Tell us in the comments what you do differently now. 👇 If you’re still doing the same old thing and not seeing the results your business needs to grow, reach out. We offer Social Media Management where we take over posting, engagement, and analytics for you OR if you like to be hands-on and want to learn, we offer coaching and trainings with our owner, Nicole. 🤩

Head to the link in our bio to learn more or inquire today.

#socialmediatips #socialmediaexperts #smm #businessowners #socialmediastrategy #whattopost
